<h1 style="text-align: center;">Mult box rentals</h1>
<p style="text-align: center;">A mult box / press box (sometimes referred to as a press box or multbox and often pronounced molt box) allows you to split audio coming from one microphone to many outputs - allowing the media a direct audio feed during your press conference. Meeting Tomorrow offers mult box / press box rentals nationwide. We carry both active and passive mult boxes / press boxes to accommodate for use with various sound systems.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Additional needs? We provide equipment, delivery and setup for press conferences nationwide. View all <a href="http://www.meetingtomorrow.com/press-conference-rentals">press conference services and rentals</a> for more information. Or call <a class="telLink" href="tel:18776338866">1-877-633-8866</a> to speak with one of our audio visual experts.</p>
