<h3 style="text-align: center;">Active mult box / press box</h3>
<p style="text-align: center;">Active mult box ideal for broadcasts, press conferences and other media events. Single mic or line-level input converts to 12 mic-level and/or 2 line-level outputs. Includes one 25 foot adaptable audio cable. No mixer is needed.</p>
