<h3 style="text-align: center;">Passive mult box / press box</h3>
<p style="text-align: center;">Passive (unpowered) mult box perfect for your press conference or other media event. Must be used with powered mixer or speaker. Single line-level input converts to 24 mic-level outputs. Includes one 25 foot adaptable audio cable.</p>
